<i>noun</i>: 탐구 [탐구], 추구 [추구], 지향 [지향] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>탐구 [탐구]</dt><br>
<dd>search; quest; investigation; pursuit</dd><br>
<dd>학문 등을 깊이 파고들어 연구함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of digging into and looking into a field of study, etc., deeply.</dd><br>
<dt>추구 [추구]</dt><br>
<dd>pursuit; seeking</dd><br>
<dd>목적을 이루기 위해 계속 따르며 구함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of following and trying to find something or to achieve one's purpose.</dd><br>
<dt>지향 [지향]</dt><br>
<dd>pursuit; quest</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 목적이나 목표에 뜻을 둠. 또는 그렇게 하려는 의지.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of striving to achieve something, or such a will.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>